    {
      "id": "2333556a-05bc-425a-8d58-1fcbe31d5ac2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Paper uses Semi-Supervised Deep Learning to perform Named-Entity Recognition on educational sections of resumes. The model predicts entities of unlabeled education sections and is then rectified. ",
